quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  43,61,"And his ˹second˺ coming is truly a sign for the Hour. So have no doubt about it, and follow me. This is the Straight Path"
  43,62,"And do not let Satan hinder you, ˹for˺ he is certainly your sworn enemy"
  43,63,"When Jesus came with clear proofs, he declared, “I have come to you with wisdom, and to clarify to you some of what you differ about. So fear God, and obey me"
  43,64,"Surely God ˹alone˺ is my Lord and your Lord, so worship Him ˹alone˺. This is the Straight Path.”"
  43,65,"Yet their ˹various˺ groups have differed among themselves ˹about him˺, so woe to the wrongdoers when they face the torment of a painful Day"
  43,66,Are they waiting for the Hour to take them by surprise when they least expect ˹it˺
  43,67,"Close friends will be enemies to one another on that Day, except the righteous"
  43,68,"˹who will be told,˺ “O My servants! There is no fear for you Today, nor will you grieve—"
  43,69,˹those˺ who believed in Our signs and ˹fully˺ submitted ˹to Us˺
  43,70,"Enter Paradise, you and your spouses, rejoicing.”"
  43,71,Golden trays and cups will be passed around to them. There will be whatever the souls desire and the eyes delight in. And you will be there forever
  43,72,That is the Paradise which you will be awarded for what you used to do
  43,73,There you will have abundant fruit to eat from